I like it. There are a couple of things that stand out, though. First, I understand that you're using a Greek character to represent the MTF name, but the articles I've read explicitly translate the unit name; hence, MTF Psi-8. Also, the twenty seven seconds required to manifest the effect seems like an arbitrary number - I understand that it is, in actuality, an arbitrary number, but still, it seems artificial. Also, it seems to me that if the effect takes 6 to 8 weeks to  a subject, and afterwards also infects the house the subject previously lived in, there's a good chance that new occupants have already moved into that property. Are they also affected?

I appreciate that amnesiacs are not effective in affected subjects. You don't see that very often, it lends some weight.







